  "title": "Administrative & Logistics Coordinator - WCAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Documentation & Catalog Management:</strong> Compile, organize, and maintain documents for submission to clients and consultants. Ensure all reports, certificates, and spreadsheets are accurate and up-to-date.</p></li><li><p><strong>Logistics & Coordination:</strong> Prepare delivery orders, liaise with suppliers and logistics providers, track shipments, and inspect goods upon receipt and prior to delivery.</p></li><li><p><strong>BOQ Management:</strong> Review, verify, and assist in preparing Bills of Quantities (BOQ) for ongoing and new projects.</p></li><li><p><strong>Administrative Support:</strong> Provide general administrative support including data entry, filing, and document management for the project team.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma in Business Administration or a related field (Design or Events background is a plus)</p></li><li><p>1–2 years of administrative experience</p></li><li><p>Strong organizational and time-management abilities</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office</p></li><li><p>High attention to detail and accuracy<br /></p><p><br /></p></li></ul><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.<br /></p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p><p>EA Personnel: Nyon Hock Sen (Aden)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124070</p>",
